Ending credits for My Little Pony: Sunny Starscout meets Twilight Sparkle
https://x.com/TheTamers12345
Director of of Spontaneous Adventure: Sunny Starscout (because why wouldn’t she be?)
Executive Galloping Producer: Hitch Trailblazer (because somepony had to keep things organized).
Chief Snack Supervisor: Izzy Moonbow (all snacks were 100% glitter-free. Probably).
Coolness Consultant: Zipp Storm (because she’s that cool).
Head of Stylish Mane Flips: Pipp Petals (she takes this very seriously).
Deputy of Questionable Decisions: Sprout Cloverleaf (who insists he’s the real star of the show).
